Do you have a passion for all things scary?

A walk that sends shivers down spines?

Or maybe you just love being part of the chaos behind the scares?

Fear Columbus in Columbus, Ohio  is HIRING IMMEDIATELY for:

🩸 Haunted House Actors (unleash your inner monster, clown, or demon)

🩸 Event Staff (keep the terror running smoothly from the shadows)

✨ No experience? No problem. We’ll train you to scare like a pro.

✨ evening shifts + the most fun job you’ll ever have.

✨ Be part of one of the largest haunted attractions in Ohio.

This is your chance to join our spooky family and create memories (and nightmares) that guests won’t forget!

💀 Apply NOW and come be a part of all the spooky fun! 

⚡ Don’t wait — the screams start soon and spots are filling FAST! 

Click the link below or in my bio for info on what it entails working here and for the application! 

Can't wait to see you <3

[https://fearcolumbus.com/applications/](https://fearcolumbus.com/applications/)

items.text:
**CALLING ALL PROFESSIONAL DANCERS! YOUR NEW SIDE HUSTLE!**

**RE:SCULPT – Instructor Auditions | London**

** **

**Think you’ve got the fire to lead from the front?**

We’re on the hunt for instructors who bring serious energy, bold vibes, and unstoppable presence to every RE:SCULPT class. This is your chance to join a brand that’s shaking up the fitness industry and setting new standards for what a reformer-inspired strength workout can be.

At RE:SCULPT, we don’t just teach classes - we *create experiences.* You’ll need to lift the room, command the energy, and connect with clients through every beat and every move. You’ll coach with precision, motivate with purpose, and deliver a workout that keeps clients coming back for more.

 

We’re looking for instructors who:
* Have undeniable stage presence and confidence on the mic.
* Understand how to blend performance with purpose - ensuring every workout has a vibe and is technically strong.
* Can create awesome energy while maintaining control and flow with the beat of the music.
* Can embrace the RE:SCULPT brand, values and community.

In return, we offer industry-leading training in the RE:SCULPT method, ongoing coaching development, and the opportunity to be part of our first **London** studio launch near **Battersea.**

Auditions are coming soon - and trust us, spots are limited.
High standards. Huge opportunity.

 

Is this for you?

Email your CV, highlighting relevant qualifications and experience, to headcoach@resculptstudios.co.uk

 
* *YOU NEED A MINIMUM OF A LEVEL 2 FITNESS QUALIFICATION, OR A PROFESSIONAL DANCE BACKGROUND.*
* *A PILATES QUALIFICATION IS NOT REQUIRED.*
* *AVAILABILITY FOR AT LEAST 2 “BLOCKS” OF CLASSES PER WEEK*

sharedPost.text:
💥 Character Spotlight: Luther Biggs 💥

Today we spotlight Tobias Armand who embodies the ruthless and unstoppable Luther Biggs — the kingpin of Philly. 💼💣
Luther takes no BS from anyone. He’s cutthroat, calculated, and runs the streets with an iron fist. Nothing moves in the city without him knowing it. 

But there’s one person bold enough to stand in his way — Detective Simone Wyatt. And she’s determined to bring him down by any means necessary. 🔥

The tension is real. The action is explosive. The showdown? Unforgettable.

🎬 Don’t miss the WORLD PREMIERE of Bullet Rush —
📅 This Sunday, October 19, 2025
📍 The Plaza Theatre – Atlanta, GA

🎟 Tickets are still on sale but going fast! Get yours now and be part of the rush!

Actors, filmmakers, & content creators… Come join us 7pm next Wednesday October 22, 2025 at [Schmidty's Bar & Grill ](https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61565475755394&__cft__[0]=AZVeHYg21suDzZXTM3jwX2r5ArEEQzvrPCcgbUKjUGQ6uUHNFH995lZGalzZmK8jbNyLqDiJO9hZrRK7nJAdU1z8XbQfsW97ybtmknpxFYmxegdaqkOzvOIScPZjkTlPOVZuSZn9ntyQwnFA-WPgvhIrToD4LMrLlfDegzc5-ZNOWDL-h72br3d9Tt_KqysniX4&__tn__=-]K-R)in Brookfield WI. 

Listen and interact with Rocky Wagonhurst as he discusses,  acting and his career, AI, media, production and his leadership at CW18 & My24 Milwaukee! He will answer your questions and discuss possible career paths ups and downs and what to do.

This is a day you don’t want to miss!

PLEASE: JOIN US let us know you are attending so we can get an accurate headcount please! October 22 speaker at meeting. See details,. Come early, stay late. Order a large pizza for 20 bucks and get a free pitcher of soda or beer. Join your filmmaker friends at this event. Open to public so please share this event. Thanks

🎭 **Queer Play Reading Club: Es & Flo by Jennifer Lunn**

📅 Tue 21 Oct | 📍 The Railway, Clapham

Join Queer Theatre & Nick Hern Books for a relaxed, queer-run evening celebrating LGBTQ+ playwriting. 🌈

*Es & Flo* tells the moving story of two women who fell in love in the 1980s and built a secret life together — now facing the hardest battle of their lives as memory fades and the outside world intrudes.

A brilliant chance to meet LGBTQIA+ playwrights, hear new queer work read aloud, and connect with **Jennifer Lunn**, who’ll join us to chat about her award-winning play.

🫖 Tea & snacks from 6:30pm | 🎭 Reading 7–10:30pm | 🍸 Social after

🎟️ Book now at

Hello All! We are currently seeking 11 people to cast for a project featuring the internet sensation Sturniolo Triplets! We prefer individuals (Male) who have a similar stature to the triplets, around 5'8 ", slim, and 18 years or older, though applicants of any ethnicity are welcome.

The shoot is scheduled for Monday from 11 AM to 4 PM in West Hollywood. Although this gig is unpaid, it offers a valuable opportunity to be featured in a high-profile video, and food will be provided.

If anyone is interested, please let me know. They can contact me at campbellchae@gmail.com. Thank you!

items.text:
CASTING CALL - PAID MUSIC VIDEO - LOS ANGELES

Project: Music Video Role: ELI (Supporting Lead) Rate: Paid Gig Shoot Date: Monday, October 20 Location: Los Angeles Area 

We are casting the supporting lead role of ELI for a narrative music video. We are looking for an actor who can portray a complex, dramatic arc.

ROLE: ELI

 • Gender: Male

 • Playing Age: Early 20s (character is a "twenty year old troublemaker" )

 • Look: "Scrappy kid with an easy smile" , "grungy but soft". We are looking for someone with a distinct look, similar to the provided reference photos (alt/skater vibe, expressive features).

 • Character Arc: This role requires significant emotional range.

 ◦ Eli begins as a "playful" , charming boyfriend with a "laid-back grin". He and his girlfriend, Bridge, share a "quiet, tender" relationship. However, beneath the surface, he has a "well of self-doubt" that deepens into a "violent, paranoid descent".

 ◦ The actor must be able to portray this "unraveling" , going from "sweet to scary" as his paranoia and pain warp him into something "unrecognizable-twisted, dangerous, and broken".�

REQUIREMENTS:

 • Must have strong dramatic acting ability to portray a "violent, paranoid descent" and "quiet unraveling".

 • Must be comfortable with MAKEUP. The role involves styling and makeup (eyeshadow) to create a "demonic" , "decaying" vibe as the character transforms.

 • Must be fully available for the shoot date (Monday, Oct. 20) in the Los Angeles area.

TO SUBMIT:

Please send the following to PINKMOOSECASTING@GMAIL.COM with the subject line: "MUSIC VIDEO CASTING - ELI - PLAYIN EXORCIST”

 1 Headshot and Resume

 2 Demo Reel (if available, please highlight any dramatic roles)

 3 A recent photo (selfie is fine)

 4 Confirmation of your availability for Monday, October 20th

Thank you! We look forward to seeing your submissions.

**Casting dzieci do filmu „Lalka” – Warszawa**
*Do kontynuacji zdjęć do filmu „Lalka” poszukujemy dzieci w wieku 4–9 lat.*
*Zdjęcia odbędą się w Warszawie w dniach 12, 14 oraz 18 października.*

**Stawka:** 190 zł za jeden dzień zdjęciowy.
**Wymagania: **dzieci muszą posiadać aktualne dokumenty PIP.

**Zgłoszenie powinno zawierać:**
- imię i nazwisko dziecka,
- wiek,
- numer telefonu kontaktowego,
- aktualne zdjęcie twarzy oraz sylwetki.

**Prosimy o przesyłanie zgłoszeń na adres:**
magda@sceneria.com.pl
**W tytule maila proszę wpisać DZIECI. **

**Jeśli jeszcze nie współpracujesz z Nami kliknij w link poniżej**
📌 Rejestracja online (dla nowych użytkowników): [https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie](https://galeriatwarzy.pl/zgloszenie)

***Casting jest otwarty dla wszystkich zainteresowanych – nie wymagamy wcześniejszego doświadczenia przed kamerą.***

**[Kraków - aktorzy]**

Do reklamy Mastercard realizowanej w ramach Film Spring Open, poszukujemy aktorów z doświadczeniem przed kamerą:
* kobieta ok 60-75 lat
* kobieta ok 45 lat
* mężczyzna około 35-45 lat
* Kobieta około 20-30 lat 

Nagrania 13 lub 14 października, godzina do ustalenia.

Projekt non profit, ponieważ całość jest realizowana w ramach warsztatów Film Spring Open: https://filmspringopen.eu/ 

Zgłoszenia wraz ze zdjęciem, i krótkim opisem doświadczenia oraz ewentualne pytania, proszę kierować TYLKO mailowo, na adres: kontakt@pawelgrabowski.pl

Do reklamy Mastercard realizowanej w ramach Film Spring Open, poszukujemy aktorów z doświadczeniem przed kamerą:
* kobieta ok 60-75 lat
* kobieta ok 45 lat
* mężczyzna około 35-45 lat
* Kobieta około 20-30 lat 

Nagrania 13 lub 14 października, godzina do ustalenia.

Projekt non profit, ponieważ całość jest realizowana w ramach warsztatów Film Spring Open: https://filmspringopen.eu/ 

Zgłoszenia wraz ze zdjęciem, i krótkim opisem doświadczenia oraz ewentualne pytania, proszę kierować TYLKO mailowo, na adres: kontakt@pawelgrabowski.pl

items.text:
Hey, everyone! I’ve been assisting with wardrobe on a local Denver feature film titled, “Blu Has a Gun” and needed to step back due to health issues. The film is already in production but needs any help with wardrobe they can get. 

Logline: To save her sister from the mob that left her for dead, a reluctant stripper must become
a more vicious monster than the ones she's hunting.

If you are interested please contact  Grant Hughes: grant@sweetflyfilm.com

Thanks!
Tracy

topComments.text: Where are you doing this work from?

Sorry you had to step back from production Tracy, it was a pleasure meeting you on the first day on set! We’re also looking for more PAs who want to learn the ropes of a bigger and more complex set! -Josh, 2nd AD

With ONLY 10 DAYS LEFT, make sure you’ve got your tickets as the countdown has begun for our highly anticipated Actors and Filmmakers Networking Event on Sunday, October 26th! Are you ready to take a transformative step in your career? This is your moment!

 

For years, Marble Academy has proudly facilitated these events. Following the incredible turnout at our June gathering, which drew over 90 attendees, we hope to build on this success.

If you haven't experienced this event before, prepare for an unforgettable time. It's an incredible opportunity to connect with talented actors, visionary directors, influential producers, and skilled crew members who are eager to collaborate on your next project. For those who have attended in the past, you know that each gathering is not just productive but also a fantastic blend of familiar faces and new connections just waiting to be made.

 

We’re also thrilled to announce that the talented Lisa Barton from Lisa Barton photography will be joining us at the event to showcase her stunning work. If you’re in need of captivating headshots, looking to refresh your current images, or simply aiming to elevate your professional presence, this is the perfect moment to make it happen.

 

Mark your calendars for Sunday, October 26th, from 2 PM to 6:30 PM at HOME Mcr, located at 2 Tony Wilson Place, Manchester, M15 4FN.

 

🎟️ Secure your ticket now and be part of something special: [https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239](https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239) 

 

Let’s make this our best event yet! Your presence will make all the difference!

I can’t wait to see you there

‼🚧Uwaga!!! Zapraszamy na casting do naszej nowej produkcji – spektaklu muzycznego „Dżuma” w reżyserii Wojciecha Kościelniaka.
Kogo szukamy?
- Trzech profesjonalnych aktorów 40+ dowolnej płci.
Wszystkich zainteresowanych aktorów prosimy o wysyłanie CV wraz ze zdjęciem do 21.10.2025 na adres 📨audycje@teatrkameralny.com w temacie wiadomości wpisując "DŻUMA - CASTING AKTORSKI". Wybranych kandydatów zaprosimy na etap praktyczny, który odbędzie się 28.10 o godzinie 14:00 w siedzibie naszego Teatru. Na etap praktyczny prosimy o przygotowanie dowolnej piosenki oraz dowolnego fragmentu tekstu.  
- Jednego zawodowego, kreatywnego ruchowo tancerza o dużych umiejętnościach aktorskich, dowolnej płci, w wieku 18-35 lat. 
Wszystkich zainteresowanych tancerzy prosimy o wysyłanie CV wraz ze zdjęciem do 21.10.2025 na adres 📨audycje@teatrkameralny.com w temacie wiadomości wpisując "DŻUMA - CASTING TANECZNY". Wybranych kandydatów zaprosimy na etap praktyczny, który odbędzie się 29.10 w godzinach 11:30-16:30 w siedzibie naszego Teatru. Na etap praktyczny prosimy o przygotowanie minutowej prezentacji solowej, możliwe dodatkowe zadania improwizowane.

📅Czas produkcji:
- grudzień 2025 (próby muzyczne)
- początek stycznia ---> 27.03 PREMIERA (próby reżyserskie i choreograficzne)
- set premierowy - od PREMIERY 27.03 do 17.04.2026 (wyłączając pojedyncze dni oraz Święta Wielkanocne)
- kolejne spektakle w bieżącym sezonie planowane są od 13 do 20 czerwca 2026.

items.text:
🚨ANGEPASST 🚨

🎬 **Schauspieler & Schauspielerin für Werbedreh gesucht (bezahlt, 750€ p.P.)**

Wir suchen **2 Darsteller (m/w, ca. 30–45 Jahre)** für **Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen im Immobilien-Bereich.**

📍 **Ort:** Hof (Bayern)
📅 **Datum:** Montag, **20.10.2025 (Start ca. 10-11 Uhr)**
⏱️ **Dauer:** ca. 5–6 Stunden
💶 **Gage:** 750 € pro Person 

**Gesucht wird:**
👨‍💼 Männlich – dynamisch, gepflegt, Business-Typ (z. B. Unternehmensberater, IT-Profi, Gründer)
👩‍💼 Weiblich – selbstbewusst, attraktiv, charismatisch, Karriere-orientiert
👉 Beide sollten den Eindruck vermitteln, erfolgreich im Berufsleben zu stehen und zur typischen deutschsprachigen Zielgruppe im Business-Kontext passen.

🎥 **Inhalt:** Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen (Business-Look, Teleprompter-Text, kurze Szenen)
👗 **Dresscode:** Business / Smart Casual

📩 **Ablauf:**
Bitte schreibt mir direkt **auf WhatsApp unter 01577 1082825**.
Wir benötigen **kein E-Casting**, sondern nur **ein kurzes Video**, in dem man sieht, **wie du vor der Kamera sprichst und dich präsentierst** (z. B. aus dem Alltag, Handyaufnahme – es geht um Ausstrahlung, nicht Perfektion).

👉 **Wichtig:**
Wir posten hier regelmäßig ähnliche Jobs – bitte schreibt mir **immer mit Ort & Datum** (z. B. *„Hof – 20.10“*), damit ich weiß, auf welchen Dreh ihr euch bewerbt.

Statister søges i Nordjylland 📹✨

Jeg søger statister til at medvirke i lidt video i Støvring/Svenstrup nu på onsdag den 15. oktober.

𝗛𝘃𝗲𝗺 𝘀ø𝗴𝗲𝗿 𝗷𝗲𝗴:

Jeg søger to "familier". 

Familie 1: En mand og en kvinde, der kan passe til en børnefamilie. Hertil også en-to børn. 

Familie 2: Et mere "modent" par (mand og kvinde) samt en eventuel hund.

OBS! Ingen store, synlige tatoveringer eller lignende. 

𝗣𝗿𝗮𝗸𝘁𝗶𝘀𝗸 𝗶𝗻𝗳𝗼: 
📍 Optagelserne foregår i Svenstrup og Støvring. 

🗓️ Onsdag den 15. oktober. Enten kl. 9.30-12.00 eller 13.00-15.00. Det aftales nærmere.

💸 Jobbet betales med gavekort på 500 kr. pr mand. 

Optagelserne skal bruges til annoncering på Metas samt andre digitale platforme til et typehusfirma. Der er tale om flere klip af et hverdagsliv i et af vores udstillingshuse.

# **SANTA WORK AT HERTFORDSHIRE ZOO**
## 🎅**Be Our Santa at Hertfordshire Zoo!**🎅

Hertfordshire Zoo is looking for jolly, enthusiastic, and festive individuals to bring the magic of Christmas to life this year as Santa Claus at **Hertfordshire Zoo in Broxbourne, Hertfordshire.**

You’ll be the star of our popular Christmas event, spreading joy and cheer to families visiting the zoo. From welcoming excited children to listening to Christmas wishes, you’ll create unforgettable memories in our enchanting grotto.

**What We’re Looking For:**
* A warm, friendly personality with plenty of festive spirit
* Confidence interacting with children and families
* Reliability and professionalism
* Previous performance or grotto experience (preferred but not essential)

**When You’ll Work:**
* 29th & 30th November
* 6th & 7th December
* 13th & 14th December
* 20th, 21st, 22nd, 23rd & 24th December

**PLEASE NOTE** - You are not required to be available to work on all of these dates. Any availability is accepted.

Shifts will be approximately 8 hours per day.

**What We Offer:**
* A fun and rewarding role in a magical setting
* £22.50 per hour
* Full costume and training provided
* The chance to work at one of Hertfordshire's most loved attractions

If you’ve got a hearty “Ho Ho Ho!” and would love to make Christmas unforgettable for our visitors, we’d love to hear from you.

Apply now by emailing **entertainment@hertfordshirezoo.com**

We are casting for our magical Christmas Grotto experience in Oxford – and we’re on the lookout for our last few charismatic, professional Christmas Elves to join the team!

📍 Location: Abingdon, Oxfordshire, OX13 5HB
📆 Contract: November – December 2025
💸 Rate: £16.50 per hour — DOUBLE PAY on Christmas Eve

✨ Requirements:

• Entry-level acting skills

• Basic script work and immersive performance ability

• Confident group singing of children’s Christmas songs

• Must absolutely love Christmas!

🎄We’re looking for:

• Confident, energetic performers with great improvisation skills

• Friendly, reliable team players

• Previous experience working with children or in character-based roles is a plus

 📌 Important Info:

• Costume and full training provided

• Paid rehearsals and site visits Early November

• Below is the confirmed list of working dates and shift times:

✅ Shift Dates & Times

1. Michalak (35lat) - 16,24.10 - przestępca, wygląda jak właściciel kantoru

2. Błażej (29lat) - 24.10 - przestępca 

3. Kicia (25lat) - 24.10 - atrakcyjna, przebojowa, dodatkowym atutem będą kolczyki i tatuaże 

4. Mariusz (35lat) - 23.10 - pijak, przemocowiec 

5. Hans (35lat) - 23.10 - niemiecki żołnierz

7. Lucjan (50lat) - 22,23,28,29.10 - lider ojców walczących o swoje prawa. Radykalny fanatyk, nienawidzi kobiet. Jego motywem nie jest sprawiedliwość, a zemsta.

🎬 Poszukiwani statyści / aktorzy do filmu promocyjnego!

Szukamy 2 osób (mężczyzna/kobieta) w wieku 23–32 lata do udziału w nagraniach filmu promującego nową aplikację.

📍 Miejsce: Kraków

📅 Termin nagrań: między 20 a 24 października

💰 Zlecenie płatne

Zależy nam, aby osoby miały widoczne tatuaże — to kluczowy element projektu.

Mile widziane osoby różnych nacji – stawiamy na różnorodność!

🎥 Film będzie częścią kampanii promującej lidera branży tatuażu.

Poszukujemy ludzi z doświadczeniem aktorskim i z dobrą energia przed kamerą.

📩 Zgłoszenia (imię, wiek, kilka zdjęć, link do profilu lub portfolio) prosimy wysyłać w komentarzu lub pw!

📸 POSZUKIWANE: 3–5 DZIEWCZYN DO REKLAMY SUPLEMENTÓW - KRAKÓW💊

Szukamy zadbanych, wysportowanych lub umięśnionych dziewczyn, które czują się pewnie przed kamerą i chcą pochwalić się swoją sylwetką 💪

Nagranie odbędzie się 18 października (sobota) w godzinach 13:00–21:00 ). Jesteś nam potrzebna tylko przez 2-3 wybrane godziny :)!

Czego potrzebujemy:

-aktualne zdjęcie sylwetki (najlepiej w sportowym outficie, siłownia vibe 🏋️‍♀️)

-podpisana zgoda na publikację materiałów

Ważną umiejętnością będzie poprawne wykonywanie ćwiczeń - takich jak podciąganie się na drążku lub używanie hantli. 💪

Oferujemy:

🎁 Wynagrodzenie barter - do 1000zł na wybrane przez ciebie suplementy

Jeśli jesteś zainteresowana — wyślij zgłoszenie (imię, wiek, zdjęcie sylwetki i krótko o sobie lub jeżeli masz sociale poświęcone swojej pracy nad sylwetką💪 )

statysta.krakow@gmail.com

MY MOMMA’S ERA: THE MUSICAL – SEEN THROUGH MY MOTHER’S LENS

Saturday, November 8, 2025
Greenwood Oasis Theater – 7621 S. Greenwood Ave, Chicago, IL
Showtime: 7 PM | VIP Experience: 4 PM | Doors Open: 6 PM
FREE PARKING

Come dressed in your best 40s, 50s, 60s, or 70s attire!
(It’s recommended — not required — for the full experience!)

Step back in time and experience a powerful musical journey through the Great Migration, Bronzeville’s rich Black history, and the soul of World War II-era Chicago — told through acting, singing, dancing, and narration.

 Featuring unforgettable portrayals of:
Billie Holiday, Nat King Cole, Ella Fitzgerald, Dinah Washington, Cab Calloway, Etta James
Plus a moving tribute to Minnie Riperton, Chicago’s own.

A dynamic cast. Real stories. Legendary music.
This is more than entertainment — it’s edutainment.

TICKETS & GROUP BENEFITS
Group rates (10+) already discounted online
Call 773-655-3575 for Senior & Youth group discounts!

Eventbrite (Use code: MyMommasEra2025):

Zeffy (No fees to us!):
 https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/my-mommas-era-the-musical-stage-play

 SUPPORT THE MOVEMENT – DONATE TODAY
Dream Real Theatre Company is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit using the arts to educate, inspire, and transform.

Zeffy (tax-deductible):
https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/donation-form/donate-to-make-a-difference-19332

 PayPal:
https://www.paypal.com/donate?hosted_button_id=4HEYR2LBTP8J8

Zelle: 773-655-3575

items.text:
PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS — NOW SEEKING FINAL CREW MEMBERS

**We’re bringing a few more people aboard an already full production team for George Orwell’s *****1984*****, directed by M.A.C.**

We’re looking for:
* **Assistant Producer**
* **Social Media / Marketing** Manager
* **Sound Board Operator**
* **Lighting Board Operator**

Performances run **December 4–7, 2025** at **Three Stories Theater (937 Liberty Ave, Downtown Pittsburgh)**.

Our **cast and crew of over 30 artists** are already deep in rehearsals and production work, and our design team has fully built out the world of the show. We’re looking for a few final team members to join the effort and help bring this ambitious production to completion.

**ASSISTANT PRODUCER**

Supports the Executive Producer with logistics, communications, scheduling, and coordination across departments. Ideal for someone organized, proactive, and interested in hands-on producing experience in a professional theatre environment.

**SOCIAL MEDIA / MARKETING MANAGER**

Join our marketing team to help manage social channels, coordinate content posting, and support our show rollout.
We already have **two resident photographers/videographers** and a **backlog of content ready to be edited, polished, and posted**. You’ll be shaping how this production is presented to the public.

SOUND & LIGHTING BOARD OPERATORS

We have professional **sound and lighting designers** who have already built out the show’s systems and cues — we’re simply looking for **two operators** to put that design work into action during **tech week and performances**.
Experience with QLab (for Sound) or ETC lighting consoles (for Lighting) is helpful, but a good sense of focus and teamwork is most important.

**COMPENSATION TYPE:** Volunteer / Possible post-show stipend
*(We want to be transparent: these are volunteer positions, but if funds allow, a small stipend may be available after the production.) *

**DATES & COMMITMENTS:**
* **Rehearsals (for reference):** Sundays, 6–9 PM starting August 3, 2025
Trust Arts Education Center — 807 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA
* **Tech Week:** November 24 – December 3, 2025 (dark day on Thanksgiving)
* **Performances:** December 4–7, 2025 (5 performances total)
Three Stories Theater — 937 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA

We’re happy to work with your schedule — please share any known conflicts when reaching out.

**TO APPLY**
Please email **playboxpgh@gmail.com** with:
* Resume (or a brief note on your experience and interest)
* Availability during tech week and performances

If it seems like a good fit, we’ll be in touch right away!

Thank you,
Marc Palombo
**PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS**

*(We want to be transparent: these are volunteer positions, but if funds allow, a small stipend may be available after the production.) *

**DATES & COMMITMENTS:**
* **Rehearsals (for reference):** Sundays, 6–9 PM starting August 3, 2025
Trust Arts Education Center — 807 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA
* **Tech Week:** November 24 – December 3, 2025 (dark day on Thanksgiving)
* **Performances:** December 4–7, 2025 (5 performances total)
Three Stories Theater — 937 Liberty Ave, Pittsburgh, PA

We’re happy to work with your schedule — please share any known conflicts when reaching out.

**TO APPLY**
Please email **playboxpgh@gmail.com** with:
* Resume (or a brief note on your experience and interest)
* Availability during tech week and performances

If it seems like a good fit, we’ll be in touch right away!

Thank you,
Marc Palombo
**PLAYBOX PRODUCTIONS**

items.text:
Projekt: Kurzfilm „Zwischen Schatten und Licht“

Drehzeit: Januar 2026

Ort: Umkreis von 200 km von Nordhorn 

Format: Kurzfilm

Gesuchte Rollen:

1️⃣ Lucy

 • Spielalter: 26

 • Charakter: Nett, liebevoll, beste Freundin von Stella, loyal und immer unterstützend

 • Schauspielerfahrung von Vorteil aber kein Muss . Newcomer sind ebenso herzlich willkommen 

2️⃣ Nick

 • Spielalter: 25

 • Charakter: Gut aussehend, charismatisch, charmant, Sunnyboy

 • Natürliches, sympathisches Spiel erforderlich

⸻

3️⃣ Felix 

• Spielalter :20

Charakter: ehemaliger Drogemjunkie,Stellas jüngerer Bruder, Geldprobleme 

• Schauspielerfahrungen von Vorteil ,gefragtes Spiel erforderlich 

Story / Kurzbeschreibung:

„Zwischen Schatten und Licht“ erzählt die Geschichte von Stella, die unvermittelt in Gefahr gerät: Victor, dem ihr Bruder Geld aus einem Drogendeal schuldet, lauert ihr auf. Als Stella Nick, einen charismatischen jungen Mann, kennenlernt, funkt es zwischen den beiden — nach einem fast stattgefundenen Kuss stürmt Stella jedoch weg und gerät direkt in die Arme des Bösewichts Victor. Nick beobachtet die Situation und kommt gerade rechtzeitig, als ein heftiger Konflikt zwischen ihm und Victor eskaliert, der in einer Messerstecherei gipfelt. Eine spannende Geschichte über Gefahr, Anziehung und Vertrauen.

⸻

Bewerbung gerne per PN

 • Foto / Porträt

 • Alter / Spielalter

 • Kurzer Lebenslauf / Schauspielerfahrung

 • Showreel

INDIAN / PAKISTANI ACTING TALENT WANTED

Must be London Based - for a PROFIT SHARE fringe theatre production running 31st March to 4th April in South Kensington, London (see image).

ROLES CURRENTLY AVAILABLE:

• ZAINAB (FEMALE/ 50s-60s) - a fiercely charismatic Daily-Mail reading matriarch (Punjabi accent) *

• IMRAN (MALE/ 30s-40s) - a young father working as a corporate accountant (Burnley accent, can coach)

• RANIA (FEMALE/ 20s-30s) - Imran's rebellious wife (Burnley or Punjabi accent - talent also needs to be able to sing)

• SAMIR (MALE/ 30s-40s) - a heavily Anglicised London surgeon (RP)

• FATHER (MALE/ 60s-70s) - Zainab's intelligent, devoted and long-suffering husband*

* Zainab and Father talent are additionally paid Equity Minimum for a day's filming work

Please email the director on reelpeoplefilms@hotmail.com for audition pieces and any further information. Please note that this is a profit-share fringe production and renumeration (other than the filming aspect) depends on ticket sales.

items.text: I’d love to pursue being an actress! At one point I was apart of a company that worked with actors/actresses. I also had representation at one point. However unfortunately I had to leave due to financial difficulties. They wanted me to get a natural representation, but the whole trip/experience would be close to $5k. Any suggestions, help, tips, or someone even who would consider being a manager for me?

topComments.text:
Hey Alicia Violeta Encinias - very sorry to hear that - what do you mean by natural representation ? Acting training ? General American accent training or a casting director workshop? 

My friendly advice is to whilst you are looking for an agent/manager is to find acting classes that will help keep your craft practiced - and yes we do sometimes invest in our career every once in a while, but the general rule has always been , don’t pay for representation ( having an agent ) and also - don’t invest what you don’t have now , 

I’d love to ask you more - details like , do you have a demo reel, resume, which country you are at - but I’m open to listen and see what o can advise you on in a conducive manner — all the best !

You don’t pay for representation. That’s a scam. Any reputable agent/manager will pick you & get paid a commission from your pay if a casting director decides to pay you. 

An agent or manager takes you on their books because you fill a gap, a type that they need & which they believe is in demand. 

Do you have a CV & professional headshots and a showreel? If you have had professional jobs put together a CV. 

The most cost effective way to train yourself is to join a community theatre (unpaid, I realise, & not for a CV but great for doing & getting experience of a range of shows, making sure you can quickly learn lines and blocking and accept direction.)

Learn the difference between stage and screen acting. Above all do your research and due diligence. 

There are lots of people wanting to take money from would be professionals for courses which lead nowhere. 

Find out the courses which end with an actors’ showcase for reputable agents. 

Find out which are the reputable industry casting directory websites which casting directors use. 

If you are a triple threat (singing, acting, dancing) you may be able to get professional work quickly entertaining seniors, singing at events, in hotels, cabarets etc. As well as researching, network with other actors, directors, filmmakers & learn about the industry from them & possible openings. 

It is a very competitive industry filled with possible pitfalls and people who have trained from very young. 

Learn about screen acting (lots of videos, books as well as courses) & approach local colleges which have filmmaking courses where you may be cast in student films. 

Join new writing groups which need actors to read out scripts. You may find this leads to being cast in some productions of new scripts & again you can network and get tips. 

Financial difficulties are part and parcel often of an acting career so if you can have a side trade that will be helpful. 

It can help an actor to do backstage work: skills in make up, design, lighting, sound, stage management, assistant directing - it all feeds into acting and gives an overall view. 

Join a union when you can - again you can draw on the wealth of experience there, they can help you with looking over contracts, advising you generally on your career. 

Watch out for red flags when asked to pay up front. 

I‘m a writer in the UK  so I‘m sure there are others here who can advise you with much more with an overview of the US industry. 

Are you able to do a reputable full time training course? In the UK there is one casting website all professional actors must be on & qualify for if they want an agent and be seen by casting directors and I am sure others should be able to advise here of US situation. 

I hope this is helpful. It may help to put at least your general location. 

You will definitely need headshots, a CV and showreel. If you join a new writing group, you may find other actors who wish to do a filmed scene for their showreel and a writer and filmmaker who are willing to do it with you. Especially since Covid, all actors need to know how to do self tapes for auditions & actors can also do monologue or even duologue self tapes for showreels. 

Above all don‘t rush in but do your research and network as well as doing as much stage, film as possible to gain experience, read lots of scripts, watch lots of stage & screen. If you can do a full time course with a good qualification at the end (again research, research, research & network, network, network to get recommendations), that would be a good springboard. Be careful about private responses to your social media posts - lots of scams & dangers - your local stage venues may also have worthwhile groups & opportunities. 

When you network you can create your own opportunities. 

Good luck!

items.text:
📣🎬 CASTING CALL - Short Period Drama 

We are casting for The Stuntman, a 3-minute period drama made as part of our final year at UWE Bristol. The film will be shot in Bristol in the week commencing 10th November 2025 (exact dates TBC). This is a student project, unpaid, but with expenses covered. The film is intended for university showcase and festival submission.

Story:
Set in 1920s Wiltshire, The Stuntman follows Ed Morris, a small-town silent cinema owner fighting to keep his theatre alive as the arrival of sound threatens to change film forever. With his fiancée Alice by his side, Ed stages one last ambitious stunt in the hope of saving his cinema - and their livelihood. A warm yet bittersweet drama about determination, passion and the march of technological change.

Roles:
Ed Morris (Lead, 28)
Charming, intelligent, and hardworking. Outwardly confident, but hiding a quiet desperation as he struggles to keep silent film alive. Needs strong screen presence and subtle emotional depth.

Alice Fardon (Lead, 22–23)
Ed’s fiancée. Feisty, loyal, and practical. She supports his dreams but occasionally shows frustration at his all-consuming determination.

Community Extras
Townsfolk gathering to watch Ed’s big stunt. A mix of ages. Families, workers and individuals. To capture the atmosphere of a 1920s local community.

Apply by: 1st November 2025
To Apply: Please send a headshot, CV (or Spotlight/Mandy link), and any showreel/self-tape to: Scarlet2.Gerry@live.uwe.ac.uk

Please include in email subject: THE STUNTMAN & NAME

We're casting the last few shifts for our magical Christmas Grotto experience in Woburn Sands – and we’re on the lookout for charismatic, professional Christmas Elves to join the team!

📍 Location: Woburn Sands, Milton Keynes, MK17 8UE
📆 Contract: November – December 2025
💸 Rate: £16.50 per hour 

✨ Requirements:

• Entry-level acting skills

• Basic script work and immersive performance ability

• Confident group singing of children’s Christmas songs

🧝‍♀️ We’re looking for:

• Confident, energetic performers with great improvisation skills

• Friendly, reliable team players

• Previous experience working with children or in character-based roles is a plus

📌 Important Info:

• Costume and full training provided

• Paid rehearsals and site visits will be scheduled in early November – exact dates TBC

• Below is the confirmed list of working dates and shift times:

TV 2 Dokumentar søger en mandlig statist i alderen 30-40 år som er ganske "almindelig" af udseende. Det er til visualiseringsoptagelser på torsdag d. 23. oktober kl. ca. 13 til 17 i Valby til en kommende dokumentar.

Optagelserne foregår på et kontor, og statisten skal spille en kontoransat. 

Jobbet er lønnet via honorar.

Passer du ind i ovenstående beskrivelse og er interesseret i jobbet, send da en mail til nyh.casting@tv2.dk med en kort beskrivelse af dig selv, evt. tidligere jobs og et par vellignende billeder.

Facebookbeskeder og -kommentarer besvares IKKE.

sharedPost.text:
Statister søges til kortfilmen "KLAGESANG"  (ulønnet)

Hej alle sammen,

Vi er i gang med en ny kortfilm, KLAGESANG, en afgangsfilm af 18 Frames, og vi leder efter statister til nogle smukke og stemningsfulde middelalderscener i Helsingør.

Vi søger:

Nonner
Torsdag d. 23. oktober
Fredag d. 24. oktober

Riddere
Torsdag d. 23. oktober

Det hele bliver optaget i dagstimerne.

Om filmen:

Klagesang er en coming-of-age kortfilm inspireret af Hildegard von Bingens liv – en sanselig og spirituel oplysningsrejse midt i middelalderens religiøse mørke.

Vi følger den unge nonne Hilde, der får visioner gennem naturen, som hendes abbedisse tolker som guddommelige.

Da den sårede Abbas – en persisk mand på flugt fra korsfarerne – søger tilflugt i klostret, bliver Hildes tro sat på prøve, og en ny form for spiritualitet begynder at spire.

Filmen er ikke anti-religiøs, men handler om tro, tvivl og menneskelighed – og om at finde sin egen vej i mødet med en verden i forandring.

Optagelserne foregår i Helsingør

Hvis du (eller nogen du kender) kunne have lyst til at være med i et spændende og meningsfuldt filmprojekt, så skriv endelig til mig

Enten her på Facebook eller på mail: livannettemuus@outlook.dk

Læs mere om 18 frames her: https://www.18frames.dk/

professionals alike, this event is an essential

launchpad for building connections, securing

partnerships, and shaping the future of film & TV.

items.text:
Spent the last several years focusing on stunts and working crew on student films, but now I’m also looking to update my acting reel to better showcase my ability. Figure I might as well throw my hat out while I’m out here submitting. 😅

I have a B.A. Acting w/ minors in Stage Combat and Voiceover, and have representation. Moved from Chicago this year, have worked commercially and previously been pinned for network shows. 😊 

ChasityCoy.com

Send any audition details/sides to CoyStunts@gmail.com or DM me. 😊

⚡️PAY WHAT YOU CAN showreel editing service⚡️

Happy Friday all! 

I'm providing a showreel service for new or established actors/directors/cinematographers/comedians/hobbyists etc 

I'm an actor myself so I know how frustrating it can be, especially when you're starting out, to collate your footage together to get more work, without wanting to spend a fortune. 

Basically, send me your footage (or I can try and source it for you if it's commercially aired) and I shall edit it together into a lovely reel. Please see samples in the link below. 

As I'm wanting to add to my portfolio it will be PAY WHAT YOU CAN 

I'll look forward to hearing from you:
reelsforanyone@gmail.com 

Thanks!

items.text:
Hi everyone, quick update to make the group more useful and less noisy 🎭

We’re introducing **Pre-Approval for Posting** for trusted industry professionals who post opportunities, services, classes and castings. If you’re an Acting Coach, Theatre, Headshot Photographer, Casting Agency, Agent, Director, Producer or similar, you can apply for pre-approval so your posts skip the approval queue.

If you’d like to be pre-approved, please fill in this short form: https://forms.gle/6MkgwGQj8sEh6QEj9

Why apply? 

Pre-approved posters have their posts published instantly (no waiting), get a small “Approved Pro” flair in the group, and help keep the feed relevant for actors.

Who we’ll consider: Acting Coaches, Drama Schools, Theatres, Headshot Photographers (headshot-specific), Casting Agencies, Agents, Directors, Producers, and other verified industry services.

We’ll review each application within 3–5 business days. 

Please only apply if you’re legitimately offering industry-related services. Spammy or low-quality promo will be declined.

Any questions, drop them below and we’ll answer. Thanks for helping keep this group professional and useful 🙏

items.text:
ATTENTION, FILMMAKERS! 🎬 Don't miss this opportunity at BBR INDIE FILMS!

​We are honored to feature Dwayne Boyd as our celebrity guest panelist! Dwayne is a CEO, a respected Acting Coach, and the founder of Premier Actors Network (PAN).

​Mr. Boyd's expertise is invaluable for filmmakers looking to elevate their projects. He's also been seen in major productions like The Hunger Games, Kingdom Business, and Nashville to name a few.

🎯 Filmmakers: Learn his secrets to getting cast, directing actors, and professional packaging. This is your chance to gain a competitive edge!

​🎃 BEST COSTUME WINS A PRIZE!

​OCT 29th | 6 PM | Studio Movie Grill. Marietta.

Tickets are selling fast: www.bbrindiefilms.com, or Eventbrite.com

​Mr. Boyd's expertise is invaluable for filmmakers looking to elevate their projects. He's also been seen in major productions like The Hunger Games, Kingdom Business, and Nashville to name a few.

🎯 Filmmakers: Learn his secrets to getting cast, directing actors, and professional packaging. This is your chance to gain a competitive edge!

​🎃 BEST COSTUME WINS A PRIZE!

​OCT 29th | 6 PM | Studio Movie Grill. Marietta.

Tickets are selling fast: www.bbrindiefilms.com, or Eventbrite.com

items.text:
Have you ever wondered why some people simply fill the room the moment they walk in?
It’s not magic — it’s presence. And it’s something you can actually train.
In this one-afternoon creative space, we explore presence and expression through psychological and theatre-based exercises. You’ll learn how to connect more deeply with your body, attention, and authenticity — whether you’re on stage, teaching, performing, or simply engaging with others in everyday life.

We're casting the last few shifts for our magical Christmas Grotto experience in Woburn Sands – and we’re on the lookout for charismatic, professional Christmas Elves to join the team!

📍 Location: Woburn Sands, Milton Keynes, MK17 8UE
📆 Contract: November – December 2025
💸 Rate: £16.50 per hour 

✨ Requirements:

• Entry-level acting skills

• Basic script work and immersive performance ability

• Confident group singing of children’s Christmas songs

🧝‍♀️ We’re looking for:

• Confident, energetic performers with great improvisation skills

• Friendly, reliable team players

• Previous experience working with children or in character-based roles is a plus

📌 Important Info:

• Costume and full training provided

• Paid rehearsals and site visits will be scheduled in early November – exact dates TBC

• Below is the confirmed list of working dates and shift times:

✅ Shift Dates & Times

• Tue, Dec 2 – 1:30 PM to 7:00 PM

• Thu, Dec 4 – 1:30 PM to 7:00 PM

• Fri, Dec 5 – 8:30 AM to 7:00 PM

• Sun, Dec 7 – 9:00 AM to 4:45 PM

• Thu, Dec 11 – 10:30 AM to 7:00 PM

• Fri, Dec 12 – 8:30 AM to 7:00 PM

• Thu, Dec 18 – 8:30 AM to 7:00 PM

• Fri, Dec 19 – 8:30 AM to 7:00 PM

📩 To apply:
Send your CV, headshot, and any relevant performance footage to: castings@evokeents.com
Subject line: WOBURN SANDS CHRISTMAS CONTRACT
Tell us a little about why you’d be a great fit & the dates you're interested in working — we’d love to hear from you!

items.text:
After the success of our last workshop we're running another at the end of this month.

Actors are you looking to earn good money between acting gigs that also keeps your skills sharp? Get paid to travel the word and even fly business class? This is all possible in the lucrative world of roleplay, where your transferable skills as an actor make you an incredibly valuable asset in the world of training and development.

Act One Roleplay has over forty years combined experience, working domestically and internationally, across a whole host of industries and law enforcement agencies such as the CIA and UK Counter Terrorism. Our team have facilitated workshops and roleplayed across five continents, playing a part in making positive change whilst earning a good living.

We will be running our three-hour workshop, Introduction to Roleplay; Witness and Suspect Interviewing on Saturday the 31st of October from 1-4pm at Theatre Deli, in central London priced at £60.

The workshop is a starters guide to the world of roleplay and what it can offer you. In small groups, we cover the theoretical aspects of the work before putting it into practice. This is then followed by a Q&A session, meaning participants leave the session armed with an immersive experience and confident in starting their roleplay journey.

If you’re interested in taking part in this or any future workshops, please contact us info@actoneroleplay.com

Old Fruit Jar Productions are casting males (40+) for The Execution of Private Slovik, premiering at @53two (21–24 Jan 2026).

📌 To apply, send:
• Headshot
• CV/Spotlight/showreel
• Self-tape of a dramatic monologue (with American accent)

🗓️ Key Dates
• 3rd Oct – Application deadline
• 10th Oct – In-person auditions
• 30th Nov – Rehearsals begin
• 21–24 Jan – Performances

This is a profit-share opportunity with funding plans to increase fees.

✉️ Send applications or questions to casting.oldfruitjar@gmail.com

Good luck!

# **WARSZAWA (wtorek 14:00 na Pradze Południe) **

Z uwagi na chorobę aktorki - szukamy zmienniczki do filmu internetowego do roli ciotki bohatera (wiek +50, atrakcyjny wygląd, dobra dykcja i brak wady wymowy, doświadczenie w występach przed kamerą). Plan zdjęciowy na jednej lokacji, ekipa operator + reżyser i aktor. Tekst prześlemy zainteresowej osobie przed zdjęciami. Płatność za około 2-3h na planie - 400zł (blik) + zgoda wizerunkowa.

**Lokalizacja:** Warszawa

 - pielęgniarek

items.text:
INDIAN / PAKISTANI ACTING TALENT WANTED

Must be London Based - for a PROFIT SHARE fringe theatre production running 31st March to 4th April in South Kensington, London (see image).

ROLES CURRENTLY AVAILABLE:

• ZAINAB (FEMALE/ 50s-60s) - a fiercely charismatic Daily-Mail reading matriarch (Punjabi accent) *

• IMRAN (MALE/ 30s-40s) - a young father working as a corporate accountant (Burnley accent, can coach)

• RANIA (FEMALE/ 20s-30s) - Imran's rebellious wife (Burnley or Punjabi accent - talent also needs to be able to sing)

• SAMIR (MALE/ 30s-40s) - a heavily Anglicised London surgeon (RP)

• FATHER (MALE/ 60s-70s) - Zainab's intelligent, devoted and long-suffering husband*

* Zainab and Father talent are additionally paid Equity Minimum for a day's filming work

Please email the director on reelpeoplefilms@hotmail.com for audition pieces and any further information. Please note that this is a profit-share fringe production and renumeration (other than the filming aspect) depends on ticket sales.

items.title: Hi,

items.text:
Hi, everyone.
Just wanted to invite you all to be part of my group for all alternative artists. I created this group with the intention of bringing together people from all backgrounds and areas of expertise to help each other create the projects we most desire. 
Although we are mostly numbered by filmmakers, as it encompasses many different skills, we're hoping for all artists to join. We hope to create a space where we can be mutually beneficial to each members' creativity and help bring our projects to life with our collective efforts.
Most members are based in the south of the UK, but we're happy for anyone to join and collaborate remotely where possible. 
Feel free to ask any questions and I'll leave a link in the comments.

**STATYŚCI - ŁÓDŹ - SERIAL**

Na kilka większych planów zdjęciowych szukamy statystów:
* **Mężczyźni i kobiety **w różnym wieku 20-80 lat - panowie ogoleni na gładko, bez nowoczesnych fryzur, mocno wygolonych boków itp.; kobiety - bez sztucznych rzęs, widocznych operacji, hybryd itp.

**Stawka: **120 zł - gotówka po planie.

**Gdzie: **Łódź.

**Kiedy: **20.10, 21.10 i 22.10.

***Można zgłaszać się na kilka dat. Tam, gdzie mogę, postaram się powtarzać te same osoby przez kilka dni.**

***Osoby, które do tej pory się zgłosiły, nadal są brane pod uwagę.**

**Zgłoszenia **proszę wysyłać na adres: LDZ.STATYSCI@GMAIL.COM

w treści podając:

imię i nazwisko,

wiek,

miasto,

numer kontaktowy,

wybrane daty,

aktualne zdjęcia,

**W tytule: "Łódź - statysta/ka".**

items.text:
**UKRYTA PRAWDA  - WARSZAWA LISTOPAD**

Poszukuję osób do poniższych ról, wybrani zostaną zaproszeni na casting ONLINE z reżyserką w niedzielę (19.10):

1. **PAULINA (43-48 lat)** - fryzjerka, zadbana, z klasą. Materialistka o dość pragmatycznym podejściu do życia. 
* 3-5.11 (dwa dni z tego przedziału), stawka 600 zł 

1. **SEKRETARKA (30-40 lat)** - elegancka, seksowna, pełen makijaż, może być mało naturalna. 
* 3-5.11 (jeden dzień z tego przedziału), stawka 350 zł 

1. **ADAM (17-20 lat) **-  szczupły, jeszcze dziecięca uroda, nikły zarost. 
* 5-7.11, stawka 1200 zł 

📩 Mailowo proszę przesłać informacje: imię i nazwisko, wiek, wzrost, numer telefonu oraz materiały: wideo wizytówkę, aktualne zdjęcia i informacje o doświadczeniu. 

Zgłoszenia kierujemy na: [patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl](mailto:patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl) w tytule wpisując nazwę roli.

**WARSAW **

**October 29th or 30th **

**(availability required on both days)**

**Rate: PLN 1200 per day**

For a **commercial for the DISPLATE brand**, a manufacturer of metal posters, I am looking for people of **various ethnic backgrounds** **as Black people, Asian etc.**

Physically attractive, with nice smiles and facial expressions. 

***Please attach your videocard / showreel as a YouTube link*** *– a short video where you talk about yourself, max 40 sec.*

Exploitation fields: Internet 

APPLY to: **ewelina.wika@podtytulem.pl**
Subject: **DISPLATE**
In the body: full name, age, phone number, city of residence, and nationality.
Attached: CURRENT photo of face and full figure. 

Portrait photo of face, in daylight, straight on, looking into the lens. Without any filters. Without glasses. Without head covering

Portrait photo of face, in daylight, straight on, looking into the lens. Without any filters. Without glasses. Without head covering

items.text:
Title: Forever Home

Genre: Horror/Thriller

Logline: A young couple tours their dream home with an unsettling real estate agent, only to discover the house holds a dark secret.

Roles:

-Raymond Russo

Age: 45-60

Gender: Male

Ethnicity: White

Description: A veteran real estate agent with a polished exterior. He is charming, articulate, and seemingly trustworthy. Beneath the polished exterior, however, is something deeply unsettling.

Requirements: Actor must be skilled with subtle menace and controlled delivery. Suited look; sharp features a plus.

-Susan

Age: 25-35

Gender: Female

Ethnicity: Any

Description: An optimistic, curious young woman who’s excited about starting a new chapter with her husband. She’s practical yet impulsive when her curiosity is piqued.

Requirements: Needs range from natural warmth to terror. Must handle emotional intensity and physical acting in horror scenes.

Production Type: Indie

Contact Information: [luke@lostefilms.com](mailto:luke@lostefilms.com)

Run Time: Short

Compensation: Paid

Union Status: Non-union

Audition Information: Please email headshot, resume and demo reel to email provided (luke@lostefilms.com). We will send a copy of the script and audition instructions.

Shooting Schedule: One short shoot day must happen as soon as possible to capture the brief exterior scenes before leaves are all gone. The other full shoot day will be scheduled close to the exterior shoot day.

Filming Location: Denver metro area

Looking forward to your submissions!

items.text:
CU DENVER STUDENT FILM CASTING CALL

Title: *Mannequins*

Genre: Thriller/Horror

Written and Directed by Archer Beck

Produced by Owen Etter

Logline: In a world where otherworldly invaders have forced humanity to live out a sitcom for their entertainment, the daughter figure in a mismatched family of strangers attempts to escape from her lifelong suburban prison.

Synopsis: In a carefully manufactured sitcom world, Daughter begins to see cracks in the illusion of her perfect family life. While she dreams of escaping the endless loop of canned laughter and staged dinners, Father insists they obey their unseen creators and preserve the family’s image at all costs. Their clash escalates into open rebellion—until Mother, torn between them, helps Daughter break free. Outside the safety of their household, however, Daughter discovers a world ruled by an even stranger, otherworldly power—and must decide whether freedom is worth the price of losing the only family she’s ever known.

Main Roles: 

**Daughter **(16-18): Eldest daughter figure who is hellbent on escaping and finding answers.

**Father **(40s): Head of the household who is trying to keep the family unit obedient to the alien conquerors that control them.

**Mother **(40s): Silent caretaker of the family.

**Son **(8-10): Golden child of the household.

Union Status: Non-Union

Production Type: Student Short Film

Runtime: 10-12 minutes

Compensation: Meals Provided, Any Transportation Fees Paid For, Film & IMDb Credit, Copy of Final Cut

Location: Denver Area

Submission Details:

To submit for audition, please send headshot(s), resumé, and reel (if available) to owen.etter@ucdenver.edu.

items.text:
Mangler i en sjov aktivitet i efterårsferien, så søger vi statister til videooptagelse på Gammelbro Camping i Haderslev.

Vi leder efter et par (alder 25-45år), som skal medvirke i en kort reklamefilm.

Vi skal filme stemningsfulde øjeblikke som gåture langs vandet, afslapning i en hytte med kaffe og brætspil. 

Optagelserne varer et par timer, og du/I vil få et gavekort som tak for hjælpen.

Dato: 14. eller 15. okt. - klokkeslæt aftales ved henvendelse.

Sted: Gammelbro Camping reception, Årøsund.

Lyder det som jer?

Send en kort besked og et billede til casting@flowerhaus.dk 

– så vender vi hurtigt tilbage

items.text:
Film Title: Clouds Have Bridges Too

Production Company: Wishing Tree Creatives

Director: Wanphrang Diengdoh (award-winning filmmaker)

Featuring: Adil Hussain

Location: Private home in Hertford

Shoot Date: Late October/ November (TBC)

Duration: Approx. 1–2 hours

Role & Requirements

Baby of mixed heritage or person of colour

Ideally: light brown skin, dark hair, dark eyes

Age: 12–18 months

The baby will portray the child of an Indian father and a White British mother

Scene involves only shots of the baby sleeping in a cot/bassinet

No outdoor scenes, no demanding or stressful filming — just peaceful, indoor filming in a gentle, quiet home environment

What We Provide & Expect

Paid role for 1–2 hours

Parents/carers must be present at all times — and are warmly welcomed on set

Calm, safe set with full health & safety protocols — baby’s well-being is the top priority

We ensure breaks, a comfortable temperature, and minimal crew

If you have a baby basket or bassinet, let us know — it may be used for the scene

To Apply:

Please email enquiries@wishingtreecreatives.com with:

1️⃣ Baby’s name, age & heritage

2️⃣ A few recent photos (in natural light)

3️⃣ Your contact details & location

4️⃣ Whether you can bring a cot or bassinet

We’re creating something gentle and beautiful — your baby’s comfort and safety will always come first.

Wishing Tree Creatives

#CastingCall #ShortFilm #BabyCasting #UKFilm #ChildSafety #FilmCasting #WishingTreeCreatives

items.text:
**DREAM. TEACH. INSPIRE. JOIN OUR BIRMINGHAM TEAM! 🌟**

 

Dance&Arts is thrilled to be growing, and we're looking for passionate **teachers** to join our team right here in **Birmingham**! If you love inspiring young children (aged 4-16) through creative and performing arts, we want to hear from you!

 

We're seeking instructors for a variety of classes. Do you teach any of these styles?

 

✅ **Dance (all styles)**

✅ **Drama**

✅ **Musical Theatre**

✅ **Basic Gymnastics (mat-based only)**

✅ **Arts & Crafts**

 

**💰 Great Pay:** We offer **£30 per hour**.

 

**IMPORTANT DBS REQUIREMENT**

Applicants must have a valid **Enhanced DBS**, or must be **willing to obtain one**. If you need to apply for one, **we will happily provide you with guidelines **for the process!

 

**📩 How to Apply:** Send your valid **Enhanced DBS and CV** to **admin@dancearts-uk.com**.

 

***Crucially, please include the position you are applying for and the location in the subject line of your email (e.g., Dance Teacher - Birmingham).***

 

Join us in bringing creativity, movement, and inspiration to the next generation in Birmingham!

 

We're also seeking instructors in **London, Nottingham, and Manchester**!

#JobOpportunity #BirminghamJobs #HiringTeachers #DanceAndArts #TeachingJobs #PerformingArts #CreativeEducation #Birmingham

sharedPost.text:
Der Kino Mittwoch auf radioYpsilon 

MOVIETIME KW 42/2025

DAS COMEBACK DES KONGENIALEN DUOS UND EIN BESUCH IN EINEM EHEMALIGEN KINO IM PULKAUTAL

In seinem zweiten Kinoauftritt taucht das Duo Pizzera & Jaus im Toplitzsee ab (NEO NUGGETS). Ausserdem haben wir die beiden in einem nicht immer ernst gemeinten Interview vor das Mikro geholt.

Vor 48 Jahren lief der letzte Spielfilm im Tonkino Seefeld-Kadolz. Anlässlich des Events mit dem Filmarchiv sprachen wir mit den Erben der Kinobesitzerin.

Weitere Filmtipps und Musik aus Filmen der letzten Jahrzehnte präsentiert Ihnen Sarah Fuchs.

Mittwoch 15.10.25 von 18 bis 19h auf radioYpsilon 94.5 oder via Stream (http://mp3.radioypsilon.at:8000/)

🌟 NOW ACCEPTING NEW FACES – CAPE TOWN 🌟
The Uzual Suspects Casting Agency is welcoming new, beautiful, stylish individuals to join our exclusive talent roster!
If you've got:
💫 A stunning, camera-ready look
🎩 Funky or formal fashion
🎬 A passion for being on screen
👠 Confidence, class, and style
Then this is your moment to step into the world of film, TV, commercials, and music videos — all PAID opportunities 💸
We’re looking for male and female talent who are ready to work and shine in front of the camera. Whether you're new or experienced, if you’ve got the look and professionalism, we want to hear from you!
📍 Cape Town based only
📲 WhatsApp Moira McKie now: +27 68 499 9959
📸 To apply, send:
1 x Professional Headshot (no hats, no shades, no filters)
1 x Full Body Professional Picture
✨ All casting work is paid. We're only looking for serious, stylish, and beautiful individuals ready to break into the entertainment industry.
Join The Uzual Suspects Casting Agency – where your journey begins.

There’s only one you — and that’s your ultimate power.

This model didn’t hide her uniqueness… she owned it. ⚡️ From the studio lights to the beaches of Maldives, her energy speaks louder than words. 🌴☀️

💎 Your unique traits aren’t flaws — they’re your signature.
VIP Models Ibiza knows how to turn what makes you different… into what makes you unforgettable.

items.text:
Have you ever wondered why some people simply fill the room the moment they walk in?
It’s not magic — it’s presence. And it’s something you can actually train.
In this one-afternoon creative space, we explore presence and expression through psychological and theatre-based exercises. You’ll learn how to connect more deeply with your body, attention, and authenticity — whether you’re on stage, teaching, performing, or simply engaging with others in everyday life.

items.text:
MODEL NEEDED FOR SHOOT IN CHESTER 📍
 
We are looking for 1 model for a restaurant photoshoot in Chester on Wednesday 8th October. The photos and videos will be used on the restaurants’ website & social media to showcase the experience of the venue.

Please comment below if you are available and meet the criteria for the shoot:
 
📆 Date: Wednesday 8th October. 
⏰ Time: 12pm-4pm
 
Requirements:
 
-       Age: Between 21-30
-       Female
-       Wearing casual outfit. 
- some playful tiktoks will also be filmed, so you must be comfortable with playful /sassy content (e.g like this: https://www.instagram.com/reel/DI4rOAITfbP/?igsh=MXd6cXFyaWtqdDdpMg==
 
💸 Compensation:
-       We have the budget to offer each model £125 for the few hours. 
- Food & drinks will be provided. 
 
More in-depth briefing will be given to those selected.
 
Please comment below if you are available and meet the criteria for the shoot and we will be in touch via Facebook DMs.

‼️ WARSZAWA 22-24-27 PAŹDZIERNIK‼️

WRACAMY DO WARSZAWY! Na plan serialu, którego akcja dzieje się w XIX wieku, poszukujemy statystów:

▪️ 22.10 pracownicy na polu naftowym (stawka 120-140zł)

▪️ 24.10 tragarze o semickiej urodzie oraz postawni strażnicy więzienni (stawka 120-150zł)

▪️ 27.10 eleganckie kobiety i mężczyźni w wieku 18-80 lat jako WIDOWNIA W TEATRZE

DODATKOWO ODBĘDĄ SIĘ OBOWIĄZKOWE PRZYMIARKI w dniach 21-22-24.10 DODATKOWO PŁATNE 60zł. Płatności gotówką po planie. 

Zgłoszenia wraz z imieniem i nazwiskiem, numerem telefonu, AKTUALNYMI zdjęciami (sylwetka, twarz-Panie z rozpuszczonymi włosami, Panowie zdjęcie włosów z boku), WYBRANYMI DATAMI przyjmujemy na adres: CASTING@ONSETAGENCY.PL w tytule wpisując „WARSZAWA”.

SPRAWIEDLIWI WYDZIAŁ KRYMINALNY

WROCŁAW

Na wtorek 21.10 szukamy aktora zawodowego lub zdolnego amatora z NADWAGĄ do roli Adwokata.

Nagrania mniej-więcej od 14.00 do 20.00

Widełki wiekowe: 30-50 lat

Zapewniamy honorarium, hotel i zwrot kosztów przejazdu.

Zgłoszenia prosimy wysyłać na adres mailowy:

igor.edwinfilm@gmail.com

Hasło: Adwokat

Zapraszamy.

Agencja Aktorska Edwin Film.

items.text:
Jarosław Janas (37) - mundurowy z komisariatu dzielnicy, gdzie grasują złodzieje. Sympatyczny, pomocny, profesjonalny i zaangażowany policjant. 

Data: 24.10

Stawka: 350 zł netto

Krzywy (19) - „herszt” bandy młodocianych przestępców. Zbuntowany nastolatek z trudnej rodziny. Tatuaże, siłownia - sprawny fizycznie, wysportowany, pościgi i ucieczka nie sprawiają mu problemów. 

Data: 22. i 23.10

Stawka: 1200 zł netto za całość

Muras (20) - członek bandy Krzywego. „Kaskader” posiadający umiejętność sprawnej jazdy na rowerze. 

Data: 22. i 23.10

Stawka: 1200 zł netto za całość (z własnym rowerem) lub 1000 zł (bez roweru)

 

Sonik (20) - członek bandy Krzywego. „Kaskader” posiadający umiejętność sprawnej jazdy na rowerze. 

Data: 22. i 23.10

Stawka: 1200 zł netto za całość (z własnym rowerem) lub 1000 zł (bez roweru)

 

Paser (44) - notowany recydywista, nie dbający jakoś przesadnie o wygląd czy kondycję fizyczną, skupiony na lewych interesach. 

Data:  23.10

Stawka: 250 zł netto

 

Sebek (16) - ofiara przestępców, kadet z klubu judo Adama. Sympatyczny chłopak.

Data:  23.10

Stawka: 250 zł netto

 

Mama Sebka (44) - przejęta losem syna matka. Płacząca, pełna empatii, troskliwa.  KONIECZNE PRAWO JAZDY

Data:  22. i 23.10

Stawka: 700 zł netto za całość

 

Matka Kamy (42) - przejęta losem córki matka. Nieco nerwowa, porywcza, ale kochająca i troskliwa. 

Data:  24.10

Stawka: 200 zł netto

Chętne osoby zapraszam do wysyłania zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl

W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci.

W treści maila proszę o zawarcie następujących informacji:

1.           Wiek/wzrost/waga

2.           Nr tel. Do kontaktu

3.           Krótki opis doświadczenia - tytuły produkcji

4.           Linki do sowich materiałów video – demo/wizytówka/scenki castingowe

5.           Aktualne zdjęcie

6.           Informacje o posiadanym i czynnym prawie jazdy lub jego braku

7.           Inormacje o ukończonej szkole aktorskiej/kursach

Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu/noclegu

sharedPost.text:
## Profils recherchés :

**DES SILHOUETTES :**

**Des hommes et des femmes de tous âges et de toutes origines pour interpréter** :
* un gérant d’aérodrome
* un pilote d’avion de tourisme (licence + certificat médical valide) 3 décollages / atterrissages dans les 90 jours
* Un dessinateur homme (35 – 50 ans) pour une doublure main
* Des jeunes filles (18 – 27 ans)
* Des pêcheurs
* Des agents de sécurité
* Des serveurs et serveuses
* Des policiers et policières
* Des joueurs de basket(18 – 25 ans)
* Des touristes retraités
* Un groupe de passants

**FIGURATION**

**Nantes et alentours : des hommes et des femmes de tous âges et de toutes origines pour interpréter :**
* Des passants  et passantes, des policiers et policières, des joueurs de basket (18 – 25 ans), du public de match de basket, des pom-pom-girls, des clients et clientes de restaurant, bar et club, un DJ et des automobilistes

**A Clisson et alentours :** **des hommes et des femmes de tous âges et de toutes origines pour interpréter :**
* Des clients et clientes ainsi que des familles au restaurant, un jeune couple

**A Pornic et alentours : des hommes et des femmes de tous âges et de toutes origines pour interpréter :**
* Des pêcheurs, des plaisanciers (si possible avec leur propre bateau), un skipper, des passants et passantes, des clients et clientes de restaurant, des clients et clientes d’un camping

**Lieu de tournage** : Nantes, Clisson et Pornic

**Période de tournage** : du 4 novembre au 13 décembre 2025

**Synopsis** :* Dévastée par la disparition soudaine et inexpliquée de son mari, Esther Bazin, capitaine de police, trouve sur sa route deux civils membres du Groupe de Recherche des Disparitions Volontaires (GRDV). La disparition de son mari étant considérée comme volontaire, la police ne peut enquêter. Esther s’associe donc avec cette brigade au profil singulier. Leur mission ? Résoudre des affaires de disparitions volontaires, « ces évaporés » sur lesquels la police ne peut légalement enquêter.*

# **WARSZAWA (wtorek 14:00 na Pradze Południe) **

Z uwagi na chorobę aktorki - szukamy zmienniczki do filmu internetowego do roli ciotki bohatera (wiek +50, atrakcyjny wygląd, dobra dykcja i brak wady wymowy, doświadczenie w występach przed kamerą). Plan zdjęciowy na jednej lokacji, ekipa operator + reżyser i aktor. Tekst prześlemy zainteresowej osobie przed zdjęciami. Płatność za około 2-3h na planie - 400zł (blik) + zgoda wizerunkowa.

Jarosław Janas (37) - mundurowy z komisariatu dzielnicy, gdzie grasują złodzieje. Sympatyczny, pomocny, profesjonalny i zaangażowany policjant. 

Data: 24.10

Stawka: 350 zł netto

Krzywy (19) - „herszt” bandy młodocianych przestępców. Zbuntowany nastolatek z trudnej rodziny. Tatuaże, siłownia - sprawny fizycznie, wysportowany, pościgi i ucieczka nie sprawiają mu problemów. 

Data: 22. i 23.10

Stawka: 1200 zł netto za całość

Muras (20) - członek bandy Krzywego. „Kaskader” posiadający umiejętność sprawnej jazdy na rowerze. 

Data: 22. i 23.10

Stawka: 1200 zł netto za całość (z własnym rowerem) lub 1000 zł (bez roweru)

 

Sonik (20) - członek bandy Krzywego. „Kaskader” posiadający umiejętność sprawnej jazdy na rowerze. 

Data: 22. i 23.10

Stawka: 1200 zł netto za całość (z własnym rowerem) lub 1000 zł (bez roweru)

 

Paser (44) - notowany recydywista, nie dbający jakoś przesadnie o wygląd czy kondycję fizyczną, skupiony na lewych interesach. 

Data:  23.10

Stawka: 250 zł netto

 

Sebek (16) - ofiara przestępców, kadet z klubu judo Adama. Sympatyczny chłopak.

Data:  23.10

Stawka: 250 zł netto

 

Mama Sebka (44) - przejęta losem syna matka. Płacząca, pełna empatii, troskliwa.  KONIECZNE PRAWO JAZDY

Data:  22. i 23.10

Stawka: 700 zł netto za całość

 

Matka Kamy (42) - przejęta losem córki matka. Nieco nerwowa, porywcza, ale kochająca i troskliwa. 

Data:  24.10

Stawka: 200 zł netto

Chętne osoby zapraszam do wysyłania zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl

W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci.

W treści maila proszę o zawarcie następujących informacji:

1.           Wiek/wzrost/waga

2.           Nr tel. Do kontaktu

3.           Krótki opis doświadczenia - tytuły produkcji

4.           Linki do sowich materiałów video – demo/wizytówka/scenki castingowe

5.           Aktualne zdjęcie

6.           Informacje o posiadanym i czynnym prawie jazdy lub jego braku

7.           Inormacje o ukończonej szkole aktorskiej/kursach

Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu/noclegu

items.text:
🎬 Hey zusammen!

Ich bin David, 55 Jahre alt aus Frankfurt am Main.
Ich bin 1,80 m groß, sportlich gebaut und vom Typ her eher südländisch & modern.

Ich habe zwar noch keine Filmerfahrung, aber richtig Lust, vor der Kamera zu stehen und in verschiedene Rollen zu schlüpfen – ob als Statist, Kleindarsteller oder für kleinere Szenen.

Ich bin zuverlässig, offen und bringe gute Laune mit 😊
Wenn jemand ein Casting in Frankfurt oder Umgebung anbietet oder Statisten sucht, freue ich mich sehr über eine Nachricht!

📧 Kontakt: teppichzentrum14@gmail.com

Liebe Grüße
Dieter

items.text:
🚨ANGEPASST 🚨

🎬 **Schauspieler & Schauspielerin für Werbedreh gesucht (bezahlt, 750€ p.P.)**

Wir suchen **2 Darsteller (m/w, ca. 30–45 Jahre)** für **Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen im Immobilien-Bereich.**

📍 **Ort:** Hof (Bayern)
📅 **Datum:** Montag, **20.10.2025 (Start ca. 10-11 Uhr)**
⏱️ **Dauer:** ca. 5–6 Stunden
💶 **Gage:** 750 € pro Person 

**Gesucht wird:**
👨‍💼 Männlich – dynamisch, gepflegt, Business-Typ (z. B. Unternehmensberater, IT-Profi, Gründer)
👩‍💼 Weiblich – selbstbewusst, attraktiv, charismatisch, Karriere-orientiert
👉 Beide sollten den Eindruck vermitteln, erfolgreich im Berufsleben zu stehen und zur typischen deutschsprachigen Zielgruppe im Business-Kontext passen.

🎥 **Inhalt:** Social-Media-Werbeanzeigen (Business-Look, Teleprompter-Text, kurze Szenen)
👗 **Dresscode:** Business / Smart Casual

📩 **Ablauf:**
Bitte schreibt mir direkt **auf WhatsApp unter 01577 1082825**.
Wir benötigen **kein E-Casting**, sondern nur **ein kurzes Video**, in dem man sieht, **wie du vor der Kamera sprichst und dich präsentierst** (z. B. aus dem Alltag, Handyaufnahme – es geht um Ausstrahlung, nicht Perfektion).

👉 **Wichtig:**
Wir posten hier regelmäßig ähnliche Jobs – bitte schreibt mir **immer mit Ort & Datum** (z. B. *„Hof – 20.10“*), damit ich weiß, auf welchen Dreh ihr euch bewerbt.

topComments.text: Eins dieser Angebote, wo man nie eine Antwort erhält, aber Daten senden soll ???

We’re looking for an actor to play **Santa Claus!**
It’s a festive children’s performance where, in the grand finale, Santa appears and gives out presents to the kids! 🎅✨

 

 Our rehearsals

November 22, 23, and 29

 

Must be available ALL of the following dates:

Performance Dates

November 30, 11:00 AM and 2:00 PM London Sloan Square

December 7, 11:00 AM and 2:00 PM London Sloan Square

December 13, 11:00 AM and 2:00 PM London Sloan Square

December 20, 2:00 PM London Stradford

December 21, 2:00 PM London Wimbeldon

 

💷 Pay: £100 for the performance

 

Apply Now:

Send your CV and a short blurb about your performance or improv experience to my 2betheatre@gmail.com.

items.text:
PAID GIG! Los Angeles locals only

Hi! I’m producing a few UGC shoots with different characters for a line of vitamin strips designed for various purposes: sleep, energy, anti-bloating, and detox.

We’re currently looking for one last character — the “gym/party guy” — someone who enjoys going out, has a social lifestyle, and also takes good care of himself.

The flat rate is $125 for approximately 3 hours of work. 

If you’re interested, please submit your headshot + video reel/UGC example. Has to be LA local as we are delivering the product ourselves. 

We’re aiming to complete filming this week.

sharedPost.text: AUDITIONS for "Scenes from the Staten Island Ferry" Thursday, Oct 16 at the Noble Maritime Museum, 1000 Richmond Rd (Snug Harbor). 6-9pm.  Need short monologue & pic/resume. If you've been in ferry plays previously, you will read from sides. This is a 2-week process. Paid. Need 8 men and 4 women. Ages 20s-50s. [Show runs in Staten Island Nov 15, 16, 21, 22, 23]

sharedPost.text:
UPDATE: THESE ROLES HAVE BEEN FILLED!

BIRMINGHAM, ALABAMA area
FEATURE FILM
STAND-IN CASTING CALL
-----------------------------
Project: FEATURE FILM - "End The Wait"

Shoot Location: BIRMINGHAM, AL area
--MUST be able to work in the Birmingham, AL area as a LOCAL HIRE!! (Travel/Transportation/Accommodation will not be provided)

DATES NEEDED:  --Monday thru Friday--
MONDAY 10/13/25 -to- THURSDAY 11/13/25
-we do NOT have exact Call/Wrap times, so you should have FULL day/night available to allow for whatever the Call/Wrap Times end up being. **MUST HAVE FULL OPEN AVAILABILITY EVERY DAY Monday - Friday to be able to work every week day as needed

NON-UNION
Rate of PAY:  $175.00 for up to 12 hours (may not work that many hours but you will be paid for the full day even if you get wrapped sooner than 12 hours)  Overtime after 12 hours (if applicable)
_______________________________________________________
ROLES: **STAND-INS**
[CAUCASIAN STAND-IN] Male or Female, Caucasian, age range 20-60, height and weight not as important as long as you have previous Stand-in experience which is REQUIRED. You would be standing in for both our Male and Female Caucasian lead actors

[AFRICAN AMERICAN STAND-IN] Male or Female, African American, age range 20-60, height and weight not as important as long as you have previous Stand-in experience which is REQUIRED. You would be standing in for both our Male and Female African American lead actors
_______________________________________________
TO SUBMIT for these roles: 
Please send us an email ASAP to - onlocationcasting1@gmail.com 
With subject line BIRMINGHAM STAND-IN
Emails must include ALL of the following:   
-First & Last Name
-Phone Number
-Email Address
-Height 
-Weight 
-Clothing and Shoe Sizes 
-Current City/State you are located in
-CONFIRM you are fully available EVERY week day from 10/13 to 11/13 in Birmingham, AL
--Please provide a resume and/or a brief description of your Stand-in experience (project, actor, length of time - please don't just say "Yes I have Standin experience")
-Recent Color Photos of you (prefer cell phone photos rather than professional headshots - NO FILTERS!) . Please include at least (2) photos - (1) Close up and (1) Full Body Standing (make sure you are the ONLY person in your photo, no sunglasses or hats)

media.ocrText: No photo description available.

sharedPost.text:
ATLANTA, GA area
REALITY SERIES
FEATURED TALENT CASTING CALL
-----------------------------
Project: REALITY SERIES - Courtroom Project

Shoot Location: ATLANTA, GA area (Dunwoody)
--MUST be able to work in the Atlanta/Dunwoody, GA area as a LOCAL HIRE!! (Travel/Transportation/Accommodation will not be provided)

DATE NEEDED:  
SATURDAY 10/18/25
-we do NOT have exact Call/Wrap times, so you should have FULL day/night available to allow for whatever the Call/Wrap Times end up being. 

NON-UNION
Rate of PAY:  $150 for up to 8hours (may not work that many hours but you will be paid for the full day even if you get wrapped sooner than 8 hours)  
_______________________________________________________
ROLES: **Featured TALENT**
[COURTROOM PARTICIPANTS] Male and Female, age range 21-70 years old, all ethnicities, wide variety of types, MUST have some type of IMPROV ability or be able to "make up" dialogue on the spot to create certain courtroom situations. You will be presented with different scenarios and expected to create effective and realistic communications and arguments.  Some scenarios will require heightened emotions.
_______________________________________________
TO SUBMIT for these roles: 
Please complete the form at: https://forms.gle/dVmYF8vPFiSUYmUu7
--or-- if you are not able to upload to the google form, send us an email ASAP to - onlocationcasting1@gmail.com 
With subject line COURTROOM Series 10/18
Emails must include ALL of the following:   
-First & Last Name 
-Phone Number
-Email Address
-Height 
-Weight 
-Clothing and Shoe Sizes 
-Current City/State you are located in
-CONFIRM you are fully available on Saturday 10/18 in Atlanta, GA
-Recent Color Photos of you (prefer cell phone photos rather than professional headshots - NO FILTERS!) . Please include at least (2) photos - (1) Close up and (1) Full Body Standing (make sure you are the ONLY person in your photo, no sunglasses or hats)
**Please ALSO include a short self-tape video (can be from your phone) - tell us your first & last name and then act out a short improvised courtroom scenario. (If file is too large to send as an attachment, please send via WeTransfer or Dropbox and NOT as a youtube link!)
